wiki.text:
'CPT' or 'Cpt' may stand for:

* Captain (disambiguation) (Cpt.), a rank or title
* CBS Paramount Television, a former TV branch of CBS now known as CBS
  Television Studios
* Certified Penetration Tester, a penetration testing certification offered
  by the IACRB
* Certified Performance Technologist, specialist in performance improvement; a
  credential offered by ISPI
* Colored People's Time, an American expression concerning African American
  timekeeping
* Columbia Pictures Television, the TV branch of Columbia Pictures
* Computerized Placement Test
* Cost per thousand, a method of calculating the relative cost of an
  advertising campaign
* CPT Corporation, a 20th-century manufacturer of word processing machinery
* Curricular Practical Training, temporary employment authorization during a non-
  immigrant student's post-secondary coursework
* Certified Piano Technician
